Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:43.60,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}心一つで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:45.75,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}生きてたらすぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:49.60,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}苦しくなっちゃうから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:52.74,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}一歩踏み出せば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.74,0:01:54.84,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}世界は変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:57.28,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}想像もしてない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:01:59.54,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}笑顔に会える
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:01.87,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}信じればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:08.78,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}僕らはできないことだって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.78,0:02:10.82,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}きっとできるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.82,0:02:13.98,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}君と一緒なら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:59.91,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}未來之事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:02.17,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}誰人能得見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:05.34,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}誰人能知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.34,0:01:09.43,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}似朝霧沉沉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.43,0:01:13.97,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}將熹光籠罩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.64,0:01:17.92,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}奇蹟之事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.38,0:01:20.80,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}將由誰創造
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:23.66,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}無人能定調
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:27.45,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}在磚瓦路上奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.45,0:01:31.44,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}於思考之前出招
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:33.49,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:35.76,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}渾身上下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:41.16,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}都在奮力呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:43.60,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}因僅憑一顆心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:45.75,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}拚盡全力生息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:49.60,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}苦痛纏身在即
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:52.74,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}只要踏出一步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.74,0:01:54.84,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}世界就會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:57.28,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}想像外的笑顏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:01:59.54,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}也能現於眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:01.87,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}只需相信便好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:08.78,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}鐵杵尚能磨成針
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.78,0:02:10.82,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}你我一定也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.82,0:02:13.98,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}只要我們在一起
